          "date": "2014-01-27 10:55:53.000000000",
          "tz": -480
        },
        "subject": "LU-2888 lov: using oi_id/oi_seq in lmm",
        "message": "LU-2888 lov: using oi_id/oi_seq in lmm\n\nSince pre-2.4 use {oi_id,oi_seq} for FIDs on MDT, which make\nit difficult to tell whether it is ostid or FID by only checking\noi_seq, so this patch will separate lmm_oi/FID conversion from\nostid_to_fid.\n\nCheck return value of ostid_to_fid, so to avoid compiling\nwarnning.\n\nSigned-off-by: wang di <di.wang@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I96b1c1a3e55d735d23e2a5fd45974e300c375477\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
